metadata.name: Damn It NFT
metadata.description: DAMNIT is a collection of 3000 unique NFTs, encouraging the free expression of emotion through community empowerment. By revivifying the emotional outburst of 3000 worldwide users, DAMNIT is a beacon of an unconstrained and free spirit for everyone. DAMNIT holders are gifted exclusive access to experiences, events, DAPPS opportunities, and more.
